title: Procter&Gamble Rises 4%
text:
Investing.com - Procter&Gamble rose by 4.23% to trade at $124.07 by 09:30 (13:30 GMT) on Tuesday on the NYSE exchange.

The volume of Procter&Gamble shares traded since the start of the session was 374.80K. Procter&Gamble has traded in a range of $123.81 to $124.07 on the day.

The stock has traded at $124.0700 at its highest and $116.1700 at its lowest during the past seven days.
